# Option A — local dev with backend on this machine: leave unset; Vite proxies /api → http://127.0.0.1:5000
# Option B — local dev hitting Hostinger API: copy this file to .env and set:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://YOUR-BACKEND.hostingersite.com
# Production (Hostinger build): set VITE_API_BASE_URL in dashboard or use hostinger-frontend.env
